snippet.title: Session - Kickstarter Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Join us November 21st for the launch of our Kickstarter campaign and write a new page in skateboarding videogame history! 
No thoughts nor wishes will bring a new skateboarding game, all together, WE will!
